oai_dc:dc.dc:title: French. Banquet ticket, September 21, 1920.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Banquet ticket. 'In honor of those who made the Volunteer State "A Perfect 36" A Banquet will be given by Knoxville Women at the Women's Building, Thursday evening, September 21, 1920, at 6:30 P.M.' Price $1.00. Lizzie Crozier French Papers.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Tickets; Banquets; Ephemera; Women's suffrage;
